\bar default

\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
tensor!angular velocity ~
\end_layout

\end_inset

：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\VecVec{E}:=\vec{e}_{i}\vec{e}_{k}E_{ik}\qquad E_{ik}:=\frac{\partial_{i}u_{k}+\partial_{k}u_{i}}{2}
\]

\end_inset

而反对称部分是 
\bar under
角速度张量 (angular velocity tensor)
\bar default

\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
tensor!strain rate ~
\end_layout

\end_inset

：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\VecVec{\Omega}:=\vec{e}_{i}\vec{e}_{k}\Omega_{ik}\qquad\Omega_{ik}:=\frac{\partial_{i}u_{k}-\partial_{k}u_{i}}{2}
\]

\end_inset

