LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:物质导数::积分展开"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 式）可以得到两种等价的 
\bar under
积分型
\bar default
 质量守恒方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\int_{V}\pdv{\rho}{t}\dd{V}+\oint_{\partial V}\vec{n}\vdot\vec{u}\rho\dd{V} & =0\\
\dv{t}\int_{V^{C}}\rho\dd{V}+\oint_{\partial V^{C}}\vec{n}\vdot\left(\vec{u}-\vec{u}^{C}\right)\rho\dd{S} & =0
\end{aligned}
\]

